ipreetidedhia: my review of Zindagi in short....now streaming for free on Flipkart videos.... its a compilation of 6 short films....each worth its while.... Starring Manjot Singh... Aisha Ahmed... Neena Gupta... Divya Dutta.. Sanjay Kapoor... Jiten Gulati...Deepak Dobriyal.... Isha Talwar... Swaroop Sampat rawal... Nidhi Singh..... films and their directors....Chajju Ke Dahi Bhalle (Gautam Govind)....was heartwarming....with an unimaginable climax.....Pinni (Tahira Kashyap) was predictable but very endearing ....neena gupta and her maid stole the show... Sleeping Partner (Punarvasu Naik) was thrilling and clever.... Thappad (Vinay Chawwal) was extremely sweet and again unimaginable climax.....Nano So Phobia (Rakesh Sain) swaroop was as always brilliant.... Sunny Side Upar (Vijayeta Kumar) was again sweet and slice of life kinds... Oscar-winning Producer Guneet Monga backing the ship..... Zindagi Inshort is an anthology comprising of 6 short stories that touch various topics including sexual abuse.... domestic violence... cross-border romance... eve-teasing... infidelity and some more.... its a scrumptious platter of varied kinds...totally worth it.... excellent performance s and totally time pass. my rating 4/5 #preetiunbiased #preetireviews #zindagiinshort #swaroopsampat #webseries #neenagupta #divyadutta #tahirakashyap #guneetmonga #ishatalwar #nidhisingh #manjotsingh #aishaahmed #sanjaykapoor #deepakdobriyal #zis
